Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:21.90,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,魔法集数院副院长 维克多·伊茨玛希已带到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.62,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,伊茨玛希
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:25.78,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,是 在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.93,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,听朕旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.88,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,为朕制作达成目标所必须之道具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,基础技术和计划表已经准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:38.52,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,汝只需实行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:43.91,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,不过 必须在最高机密环境下实行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:48.80,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,已在国外准备好研究据点和资金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.20,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,马上去办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.27,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:56.02,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,还有件事 需要让汝知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.06,Default,Izhmash,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:03.55,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,一切皆为朕而动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.75,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,即便看似背道而驰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.53,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,而那正是 朕的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.98,Default,Gaz,0,0,0,,朕命不久矣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:22.25,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,五年前 我们六国联合军中编制出的八英雄 讨伐了贾兹皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:40.14,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,至此 绵延三百年的战争 虽然画上了休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,战后 时至五年够的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:47.11,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,曾有禁断皇帝之称的贾兹皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:50.28,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,仍对这片大地有着深远的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:55.27,Default,Ivanov,0,0,0,,和不久前的航天要塞事件也有关？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:00.73,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,皇帝的遗体和其女──嘉依卡算是开端
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:05.03,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Isan, hizan, yadwavi, ama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:07.30,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 压缩制御之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.72,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【过载者】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.31,Default,Chaika,0,0,20,,{\an8}Elum... Naikt inte... Naint...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.44,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,如诸位所知 一个月前发生的航天要塞事件中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:30.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,不仅将军及众多将士殉职 还让事态发展至战争边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:32.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,肆虐吧 狂风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:34.66,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【唤风者】
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:39.79,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,担任战后复兴推进的克里曼机关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:43.40,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,康拉德机关长 请报告详细情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.24,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.61,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,加瓦尔尼公爵之子里加尔图·加瓦尔尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:53.54,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,应该是利用贾兹皇帝遗体驱动的航天要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:05:00.65,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,据前去调查的队员报告 遗体来源应该是名叫嘉依卡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:12.45,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,自称嘉依卡的女孩开始在大陆各地出现 是战争结束三年后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.07,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,不论其虚实
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,她们全都以收集八英雄手中的皇帝遗体为目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.83,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你真是贾兹皇帝的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.42,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 本尊 真正的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:31.08,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你父亲不是最强的魔法师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:33.67,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Elum... Naikt inte... Naint...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.47,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Bertolt... Infant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:37.76,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,显现吧 狂虐的涡旋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.06,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【占星者】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:46.23,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,惊人 咒文 时间短
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:53.74,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:56.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Elum... Kolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.18,0:05:58.57,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 爆破消散之物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:05:59.95,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【破坏者】
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:00.62,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Natow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.92,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,他们当过兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.42,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,蹲在这乡下干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.97,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,貌似都很擅长用武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.06,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.37,Default,Both,0,0,0,,吾即为钢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:21.56,Default,Both,0,0,0,,吾钢故无畏 吾钢故无惑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:24.87,Default,Both,0,0,0,,若敌当前 变舍弃一起切顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:26.77,Default,Both,0,0,0,,吾乃灭敌之凶器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:28.77,Default,Both,0,0,0,,铁血转化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.41,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.33,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你们俩 那个外表…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.44,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,我在战场上见过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.71,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,战魔众的乱破师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:48.83,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.71,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,为什么要帮贾兹皇帝的女儿偷遗体？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.80,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不是帮 是目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:58.05,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,那家伙的目的 就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:11.44,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你们手生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.61,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,看来那边打完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.91,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,很可惜 貌似你从我这抢不走遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.16,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【冲击者】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:39.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,怕什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:41.22,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,一开始就说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.72,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,要比个高下 但不必你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.64,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,完全的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.40,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,我怎么说也曾是个英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:54.14,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,比你经历的多太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.54,0:07:54.90,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.30,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那边是你们赢了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.32,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,真够小瞧我们的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.36,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,一胜一负 今天就算打平了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:08.29,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,明天再比一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.83,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,再战 十分欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:21.78,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁 阿卡莉 推荐尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.46,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊咧 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:26.50,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,刚才失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:31.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这怎么做生意？驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.36,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,请您鉴定葡萄酒的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:39.75,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,葡萄园经营者 而且有酒窖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:42.74,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,完全是人生赢家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.14,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,葡萄也好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.90,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,人生葡萄两丰收吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.20,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长 羡慕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.91,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,我很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.29,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,看着兄长想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是觉得没什么能比家庭和安居之所更值得拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.17,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.56,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,快看 那生龙活虎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.05,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯 她真的是英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.82,0:09:09.34,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不认识的人 不说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.13,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,只是有遗体 不一定是英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:15.63,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅女士确实是八英雄之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.92,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,但那已经是过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:23.99,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,如今为经营这个酒窖 过着日夜操劳的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:27.87,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,战争结束后 流落街头的士兵们自不必提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:33.21,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,连各地失去曙光的人马 都从她这得到了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.09,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,真是位奇特的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:42.40,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,所以几位突然造访 要求赌上遗体进行比试…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:47.78,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,而且那东西 对珂罗蒂雅女士而言 就好比勋章
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:49.09,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,添麻烦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.27,Default,Butler,0,0,0,,添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:53.97,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,又不是勋章 不算添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:58.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,而且比试是我提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:02.47,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这个酸味适中 挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.31,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,南侧田可以收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.51,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,北侧还不行 得再等几天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:09.37,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.69,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,如你所见 我这很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.50,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,所以明天加个时限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.96,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你们三人一起上 从午饭后到下午茶前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:23.87,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,只要能胜我一招 就算你们赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.26,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.39,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,自称嘉依卡的女孩收集贾兹皇帝遗体的传闻我听过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.48,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,没想到都找到我这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.96,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那可是很强的魔法思念料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.03,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,听说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:50.66,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,有嘉依卡要用遗体做出的武器找六国联合报杀父之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:52.99,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,装在那个里面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.25,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯 已经收集到多个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.90,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你 打算怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.50,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲 凭悼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:05.89,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是吗 作为女儿 会这么想也在所难免啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.97,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,父亲临终 什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.51,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,临终…我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.53,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,因为在照顾受伤的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.00,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你没看到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.23,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,但是 最后一击是讨伐队队长的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.84,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那是 他…应该把皇帝女儿的头也砍掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.84,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这么说…死掉的女孩是假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.41,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.84,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,对了对了 告诉你点有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:45.20,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,你的魔法尽是攻击 忽略了防守对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.42,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,得加强防守才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:48.36,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:51.57,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,还有 咒文咏唱太长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:57.68,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,选出必要词句 简短的咒文 也能发动魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:11:59.87,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,忠告 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.44,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 努力 必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:04.66,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,这么坦诚 我都不自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.58,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊 喝葡萄酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.74,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不 明天还要比试 心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.95,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,啊咧 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.29,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,美味？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,一杯 请求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:16.66,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,明天下午为止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.30,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,时间不太充裕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:38.03,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,要我们三对一 听着虽说像吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:41.81,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,阿卡莉 咱如果不好好制定战术 恐怕会危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.82,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.39,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅是英雄兼身手不凡的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:54.84,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,包括管家和秘书在内 酒窖工作的人 都是有两下子的退伍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:55.45,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:13:00.70,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,因此 我们是要在强敌包围中度过一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.33,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长一定很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.33,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,但是不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:09.17,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,今晚就这样 让我紧贴着兄长入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.63,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.62,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,咒文简化 难题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.18,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,确实 那人的咒文短的离谱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.82,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,那是经验所致吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:30.02,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:33.72,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,得一如既往 由我和兄长拖延时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.08,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.76,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅 转眼间 托鲁你们 妨碍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.16,0:13:40.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我们被封住行动就完蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.00,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,这样一来 得有陷阱才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.17,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,真麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:47.67,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:53.51,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,不如托鲁跟我结下契约 变成龙骑士 不就能轻松取胜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.28,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,又提这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.83,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,问我雇主去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.09,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.22,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,心意 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.94,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是珂罗蒂雅的条件 对战 三对一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.23,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,赢了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.55,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,你想要遗体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:11.95,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.76,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,嗯…真老实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.74,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,托鲁也总纠结于乱破师的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.26,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,真没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.66,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,我哪有纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.62,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,嘛 算了 改变主意的话随时告诉我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:30.53,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,芙蕾多妮卡 你在贾兹帝国讨伐战时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.58,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,既然跟珂罗蒂雅打过交道 知不知道她的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.27,Default,Fredrica,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是同伴 又没交过手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:38.11,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:43.27,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:47.47,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,明天再战之前 抓紧一切时间特训魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:48.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:52.86,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,话说 咒文有啥意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:58.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这世上之物 一起存在 都有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:04.20,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,气温 水分 风向 地脉 等等一切 影响魔法的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:06.91,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法发动 条件众多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:09.37,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,正确咒文 需要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:13.81,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法思念料内 仍残存已死生物的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:20.39,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法师的强烈思绪 通过准确咒文 思念料里的记忆 抽出可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:22.75,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法 换个说法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,生物的记忆 思念 消耗掉 引发现象的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:33.02,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,贾兹皇帝遗体被称为最强魔法思念料 这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:38.55,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,魔法思念料 记忆 其中思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:42.99,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,大概 父亲生前的思绪 极其强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.95,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显示咒文简化 挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:49.54,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,咒文 类似句 多数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:51.58,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 尝试重新组合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.91,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这个…听着就不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:55.96,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:58.17,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,最重要的咒文是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:01.84,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:03.35,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,现在查阅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.81,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,这来得及吗 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.77,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Lai braga... Iatavi... Kamal al...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:11.98,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Ifun... Elstel... Rankali... Bunkali...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.45,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Roh... Task... Am... Il...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.44,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Glokka! Tamult!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.17,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Naints... Ahman... Isaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.46,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Flakinekt... Trinelil...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.38,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,前路漫漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.77,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,报告我已经读了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:53.65,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,关于基列特队长 实际当地 究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.30,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,队长他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.07,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,在航天要塞事件时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.49,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,为了救航天要塞中的芷依塔和薇薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.99,Default,Setra,0,0,0,,混账 你是何居心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:10.58,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,无论如何也要请您延缓攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.54,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,结果 战斗突然开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:14.62,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,基列特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:16.21,Default,Gillette,0,0,0,,快逃 李奥纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.80,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,队长被卷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.47,Default,Leo,0,0,0,,得知实情的薇薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:23.43,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:28.31,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,薇薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:37.27,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,在你们面前 变得…像嘉依卡一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.19,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:42.98,Default,Matheus,0,0,0,,追捕嘉依卡的人 居然变成嘉依卡的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:44.43,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,她为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:50.12,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,为确认是否与贾兹皇帝有渊源 我查了她的履历
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.95,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,她说自己是孤儿 从小被培养成暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.25,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,然后被贵族收作了护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:01.25,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,嗯 此外 血缘并不明确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.65,0:18:05.28,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,总之 从航天要塞一事看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:11.52,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,嘉依卡的存在与皇帝遗体会给大陆带来巨大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:13.35,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:17.76,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,你们由尼克拉接任队长 维持队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:20.15,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,继续搜寻嘉依卡的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.11,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.51,0:18:28.49,Default,Nikolai,0,0,0,,但是 部队名请维持基列特队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.89,0:18:30.70,Default,Konrad,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.69,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:54.10,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,奇伊 暂且算是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:58.63,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,由于被大家介入 你只有一半变成了嘉依卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:02.03,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,但是仍有嘉依卡的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.63,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,闭嘴 我才不是禁断皇帝的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,不愿承认啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.66,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,但这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,嘛 一半也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.42,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,只要能完成嘉依卡的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:15.41,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,使命？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.45,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,收集皇帝遗体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.67,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.49,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.50,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,收集全了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.14,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,你 是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.45,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,情报提供者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.10,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.98,Default,Zita,0,0,0,,薇薇 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:48.48,Default,Vivi,0,0,0,,我…才不是嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:56.77,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.27,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,咒文简化 不顺利 极其不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:04.39,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 取胜信心 全无
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:08.08,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不必担心 遗体肯定帮你夺到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.75,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,兄长说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:14.60,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,就算比试没赢 也知道了遗体所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.43,0:20:17.01,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不行就用偷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:19.84,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,心意 感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:22.86,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是我 作为魔法师战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:28.94,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:30.71,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:42.48,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,昨晚貌似魔法练到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.21,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,有成果了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.26,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:49.62,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是吗 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.15,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,但是我 全力战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.93,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,而且 托鲁和阿卡莉 战斗力 信任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:58.89,Default,Toru,0,0,0,,不论用什么手段 也要拿走遗体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:01.35,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,像乱破师的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.34,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,托鲁和阿卡莉 乱破师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.19,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,同时 我珍视的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.94,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,是吗 有可靠的同伴值得高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:11.55,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.41,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,准备 万全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.45,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,那 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:27.17,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,Furom, iestrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:28.71,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Elmuto... Eril!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:31.80,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,Natow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:33.59,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,显现吧 【暴风】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.83,Default,Akari,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:38.56,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,显现吧 紧绷的大气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:40.68,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,【迷途者】
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.08,0:21:41.93,Default,Claudia,0,0,0,,【老绅士】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.82,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,珂罗蒂雅的教诲 实在有益
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.63,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 努力 绝不吝啬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:33.04,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,这宅子 全是葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:35.00,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,蛋糕 饼干 馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.17,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,我 想住下来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.95,Default,Chaika,0,0,0,,下集 魔法师的尊严
